source.name: NSF Freedom of Information Act Report for October 1, 2008 through September 30, 2009
source.description: Statistical information on the number of FOIA requests received and processed by NSF in FY09, response times for FOIA requests, the number of appeals received, and other statistics on NSF's FOIA program.
